3 ± 0.684 15.043 ± 0.351 18.802 ± 1.216 17.259 ± 1.320 RMSE 19.075 ± 0.751 18.580 ± 0.244 23.610 ± 2.059 21.171 ± 1.141 R 2 0.308 ± 0.055 0.344 ± 0.017 -0.067 ± 0.188 0.146 ± 0.090improvements in prediction performance highlight the effectiveness of distribution alignment during the pretraining stage, which enhances the generalization capability of models.",
